{"tid":430774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑休班時遭同袍搜出身上藏K仔 休班警被控藏毒今提堂","createTime":"2017-10-10T05:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T16:58:01.000Z","uid":5195,"like":84,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"e4f27999c23bfb6f0436ecf131832a6aad90ce35","tid":430774,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T05:59:16.000Z","msg":"男警休班期間在街頭遇上同袍截查，被搜出身上涉藏有少量毒品氯氨酮(俗稱K仔)。警員被控藏毒罪，案件今在西九龍裁判法院提堂，被告申請押後答辯，獲准保釋候訊。<br />\n<br />\n被告潘俊東（40歲）聘用私人律師代表，他被控於去年10月28日在荃灣綠楊新邨D座旁的行人路管有危險藥物，即0.38克氯胺酮。被告獲准保釋至11月14日再訊。"},{"pid":"6908239a7030d7047f80a1c4b40e3b430ff8b605","tid":430774,"uid":17081,"like":151,"dislike":1,"score":150,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:00:24.000Z","msg":"警超聯積分榜召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd2b03113ac37251150f046f76da46a959b4f83","tid":430774,"uid":82720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:05:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警超聯積分榜召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f8c8f57deb2eb5b5cd1167b675d69f816f78d606","tid":430774,"uid":118132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:05:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>警超聯積分榜召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d8725429bbdb9ba361b5396bc16c16766cd65c9c","tid":430774,"uid":30169,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:06:24.000Z","msg":"Goal ~~~"},{"pid":"76db85f53bf966c5cd75ec3535d3aed8ac1353ca","tid":430774,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:07:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>警超聯積分榜召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"95b5a09e13347339ba7a469d2bd7d5b550a22720","tid":430774,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":24,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:10:21.000Z","msg":"